{
  "name": "StoreKit2Manager",
  "version": "1.0.4",
  "summary": "一个简洁、易用的 StoreKit2 封装库，提供统一的接口来管理应用内购买",
  "description": "StoreKit2Manager 是一个基于 StoreKit 2 的封装库，提供了简洁易用的 API 来管理应用内购买。\n\n主要特性：\n- 配置驱动，易于集成\n- 支持协议回调和闭包回调两种方式\n- 自动监听交易状态变化\n- 完整的错误处理\n- 支持所有产品类型（消耗品、非消耗品、订阅等）\n- 线程安全，所有回调在主线程\n- 订阅产品国际化支持（标题、副标题、按钮文案）\n- 优惠代码兑换支持\n- 家庭共享检测",
  "homepage": "https://github.com/ppswdev/StoreKit2Manager",
  "license": {
    "type": "MIT",
    "file": "LICENSE"
  },
  "authors": {
    "ppswdev": "xiaopin166@gmail.com"
  },
  "platforms": {
    "ios": "15.0"
  },
  "swift_versions": "5.9",
  "source": {
    "git": "https://github.com/ppswdev/StoreKit2Manager.git",
    "tag": "1.0.4"
  },
  "source_files": [
    "StoreKit2/StoreKit2Manager/StoreKitManager.swift",
    "StoreKit2/StoreKit2Manager/Models/**/*.swift",
    "StoreKit2/StoreKit2Manager/Protocols/**/*.swift",
    "StoreKit2/StoreKit2Manager/Internal/**/*.swift",
    "StoreKit2/StoreKit2Manager/Locals/**/*.swift",
    "StoreKit2/StoreKit2Manager/Converts/**/*.swift"
  ],
  "exclude_files": [
    "StoreKit2/StoreKit2Manager/Docs/**/*"
  ],
  "frameworks": [
    "Foundation",
    "StoreKit",
    "Combine"
  ],
  "ios": {
    "frameworks": "UIKit"
  },
  "osx": {
    "frameworks": "AppKit"
  },
  "requires_arc": true,
  "module_name": "StoreKit2Manager",
  "swift_version": "5.9"
}
